<div class="landing-container">
  <div class="landing-text">
    <h1>Welcome to Soluna: a messaging app</h1>
    <div class="landing-text-definition">
      <p>"Soluna" takes the inspiration from the Spanish words  <em>"sol" (day) and "luna" (night)</em>, blending them into a messaging vibe where you can chat around the clock. 🌞🌙 </p>
    </div>
    <p>
      Step into Soluna, where messaging transcends the ordinary, creating an immersive group chat experience that opens the door to new connections and vibrant conversations. 🌐
    </p>
    <p>
      Soluna isn't just about sending texts; it's a social catalyst that brings people together in dynamic group chats, fostering an environment where meeting new faces becomes an exhilarating journey.
      Our platform seamlessly merges cutting-edge technology with an effortlessly user-friendly design, making every interaction a joyous experience.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="landing-banner">
    <%= image_tag('group-chat.avif', alt: 'Message Banner') %>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="title">
  <h3>🌟 Welcome to Soluna - Our Community Guidelines 🌟</h3>
</div>
<div class="house-rules">
  <div class="card">
    <h5>Be Kind and Respectful ✨</h5>
    <p>
      Spread positivity!
      Treat everyone with kindness and respect. Let's create a space where everyone feels valued.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <h5>Privacy is Key 🔒</h5>
    <p>
      Keep it personal, just not too personal.
      Protect your own privacy and that of your fellow Solunians.
      Think twice before sharing anything too personal.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <h5>No Spam, Just Love 🚫📢</h5>
    <p>
      We're all here for great conversations, not for promotions.
      Save the advertising for designated spaces, and let's keep our chats spam-free.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <h5>Keep it Classy 💬</h5>
    <p>
      Keep the vibes positive, avoid inappropriate content, and if you see something off, report it to our friendly moderators.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <h5>Feedback and Suggestions 🗣️</h5>
    <p>
      Your feedback is gold!
      Share your ideas, suggestions, and thoughts.
      Help us make Soluna the best it can be. Your voice matters!
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <h5>And Finally... Enjoy! 🌟</h5>
    <p>
      Soluna is your space to connect, chat, and enjoy. Soak in the positive energy and make every interaction a joyful one!
      Thank you for being an awesome part of Soluna! 🚀✨
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
